            "title": "A股低開 窄幅偏軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股低開後偏軟。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指開報3397點，跌5點或0.15%，現報3397，跌4點或0.12%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指開報10193點，跌41點或0.4%，現報10196，跌38點或0.38%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300開報3881點，跌11點或0.28%，現報3878，跌3點或0.35%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數開報2054點，跌13點或0.63%，現報2062，跌4點或0.19%。</p>\n</div>",
